description: Use Belkin's Micro Usb cable to charge any phone with a micro charging port. Use it to sync your micro to usb compatible phone with your computer. Transfer data from your phone to your computer and the other way around! Great for anyone who owns one or several of the million devices out there that rely on the micro port for charging and syncing.
title: Belkin 3-Feet Micro to Usb Cable (F3U166-03)
